Firedrill came to the grim realization, but he was to slow, "No, come
back with Cliffjumper." he screamed, quickly jumping into the air, then
turning his body to land on his stomach. Instead of landing though, he
transformed, and landed on already reved wheels, as he peeled out as
fast as he could, following the captors. 

Grimlock pulled himself up, and saw Strafe being kidnapped. "Grrr, no
Autobot taken prisoner while Grimlock in charge, NO." he yelled, and
didnt wait for permission from Pacifix, as he launched himself into the
air, like a bombastic missile, following the Obeytis ship.
